728389f-a.folder: Arthur Kill Road & Arden Avenue, Staten Island, NY

728370f-a.title: Richmond: Arthur Kill Road - Arden Avenue
728370f-a.text:
1765 and 1767 Arthur Kill Road, north side,
adjoining the N.E. corner of Arden Avenue, showing
tenements that belonged to The Rossville Brick Company
whose factory was located directly in back of the houses.
The view is southward toward Arden Avenue.
May 5, 1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REFRODUCTIONS
728370f-a.folder: Arthur Kill Road & Arden Avenue, Staten Island, NY

728388f-a.title: Richmond: Arthur Kill Road - Arden Avenue
728388f-a.text:
Arthur Eill Road, north side, east of Arden Ave., ahowing the
J. Mills house. The house is about 660 yards back of the road near
Benedicts Creek.
April 9, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
